title: E117 NIPSEY HUSSLE CONVINCED GASHI TO DROP OUT OF SCHOOL - IMPAULSIVE EP. 117
itunes:title: NIPSEY HUSSLE CONVINCED GASHI TO DROP OUT OF SCHOOL - IMPAULSIVE EP. 117
description:
Multi-platinum Albanian artist GASHI walks around with $50,000 in his bag, international clout and a record deal with RCA Records... however, just one decade ago, he was broke, on the verge of suicide, and about to quit music. With hit songs like "My Year" and "Creep on Me," GASHI now tours the world performing for his global audience. Stay tuned for his live performance of his new single, "SAFETY."

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
